<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 00:54:24 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>新总统上任几天后，中国开始在台湾周围进行军事演习</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-starts-military-drills-around-taiwan-days-after-new-president-takes-office-2024-05-23/</link><description>中国军方周四早些时候开始围绕台湾进行联合演习，预计将持续到周五，就在台湾新总统赖清德上任并呼吁北京停止威胁的几天后。</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 00:35:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-starts-military-drills-around-taiwan-days-after-new-president-takes-office-2024-05-23/</guid></item><item><title>桥水基金任命中国区总裁阿尔珀特负责监管新投资部门</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/bridgewater-taps-china-head-alpert-oversee-new-investment-unit-2024-05-22/</link><description>桥水基金已提拔其中国区总经理乔安娜·阿尔珀特 (Joanna Alpert) 担任最近成立的业务部门负责人，该部门专注于管理和创造新的投资产品。</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 23:55:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/bridgewater-taps-china-head-alpert-oversee-new-investment-unit-2024-05-22/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞标：韩国银行紧随其后，英伟达继续前进</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-05-22/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 21:50:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-05-22/</guid></item><item><title>杜邦公司将分拆为三个公司，并更换首席执行官埃德·布林 (Ed Breen)</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/dupont-separate-into-three-independent-companies-2024-05-22/</link><description>杜邦公司周三表示，将分拆为三家上市公司，其股价在盘后上涨 5%，加入众多寻求释放价值和追求集中增长的美国企业集团行列。</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 21:10:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/dupont-separate-into-three-independent-companies-2024-05-22/</guid></item><item><title>独家：消息人士称，因国家监管机构审查而推迟波音向中国交付</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/boeing-deliveries-china-delayed-by-state-regulator-review-source-says-2024-05-22/</link><description>一位知情人士告诉路透社，由于中国对驾驶舱录音机电池进行监管审查，波音向中国的飞机交付最近几周被推迟。</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 19:52:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/boeing-deliveries-china-delayed-by-state-regulator-review-source-says-2024-05-22/</guid></item><item><title>美国立法者提出法案，以更容易遏制人工智能模型的出口</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-lawmakers-advance-bill-make-it-easier-curb-exports-ai-models-2024-05-22/</link><description>众议院外交事务委员会周三以压倒性票数通过了一项法案，该法案将使拜登政府更容易限制人工智能系统的出口，理由是担心中国可能利用这些系统来增强其军事能力。</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 17:01:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-lawmakers-advance-bill-make-it-easier-curb-exports-ai-models-2024-05-22/</guid></item><item><title>中国地方政府机构要求恒大电动汽车公司返还2.624亿美元补贴</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-local-bodies-ask-evergrande-ev-unit-return-2624-mln-subsidy-2024-05-22/</link><description>中国恒大新能源汽车周三表示，其子公司已收到中国地方行政机构的一封信，要求偿还作为补贴和奖励提供的19亿元人民币（2.6242亿美元）。</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 14:19:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-local-bodies-ask-evergrande-ev-unit-return-2624-mln-subsidy-2024-05-22/</guid></item><item><title>法国七国集团需要在中国产能过剩问题上团结一致</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/g7-needs-stand-united-chinese-overcapacity-france-2024-05-22/</link><description>法国财政部长布鲁诺·勒梅尔周三在与七国集团同行举行会议之前表示，面对中国在电动汽车电池等关键行业的产能过剩，七国集团经济强国需要团结起来。</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 13:04:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/g7-needs-stand-united-chinese-overcapacity-france-2024-05-22/</guid></item><item><title>中国多个城市大幅降低还款额和抵押贷款利率以刺激房地产需求</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/several-chinese-cities-slash-down-payments-mortgage-rates-boost-property-demand-2024-05-22/</link><description>据官方媒体报道，中国多个城市降低了首付和抵押贷款利率，以应对最新一波刺激低迷房地产需求的刺激措施。</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 11:20:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/several-chinese-cities-slash-down-payments-mortgage-rates-boost-property-demand-2024-05-22/</guid></item><item><title>英国国防部长称中国正在努力向俄罗斯提供致命援助</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk-defence-minister-says-china-working-supply-lethal-aid-russia-2024-05-22/</link><description>英国国防部长格兰特·沙普斯周三指责中国向俄罗斯提供或准备向俄罗斯提供致命援助，用于其对乌克兰的战争。</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 10:46:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/uk-defence-minister-says-china-working-supply-lethal-aid-russia-2024-05-22/</guid></item><item><title>Temu母公司拼多多控股第一季度营收超出预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/temu-operator-pdd-holdings-beats-first-quarter-revenue-estimates-2024-05-22/</link><description>拼多多控股周三超出了第一季度收入预期，这得益于其国际购物网站特木以及消费者对其中国折扣电子商务平台拼多多日益增长的兴趣。</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 10:42:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/temu-operator-pdd-holdings-beats-first-quarter-revenue-estimates-2024-05-22/</guid></item><item><title>格罗西表示，伊朗总统去世推迟了与国际原子能机构的谈判</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/death-irans-president-has-delayed-talks-with-iaea-grossi-says-2024-05-22/</link><description>伊朗总统和外交部长在直升机失事中丧生，导致联合国核监督机构与德黑兰就改善与该机构合作的谈判暂停，该机构负责人拉斐尔·格罗西周三对路透社表示。</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 10:39:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/death-irans-president-has-delayed-talks-with-iaea-grossi-says-2024-05-22/</guid></item><item><title>新兴市场信用评级终于再次回升</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/emerging-market-credit-ratings-are-finally-looking-up-again-2024-05-22/</link><description>从巴西、尼日利亚和土耳其，甚至到埃及和赞比亚等一些风险最高的新兴市场，越来越多的证据表明，长达十年的主权信用评级恶化终于开始扭转。</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 10:12:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/emerging-market-credit-ratings-are-finally-looking-up-again-2024-05-22/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：英伟达临近，英国 CPI 大幅上涨未达到目标</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-05-22/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 10:04:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-05-22/</guid></item><item><title>流亡中国商人郭文贵因诈骗罪受审</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/legal/exiled-chinese-businessman-guo-wengui-goes-trial-fraud-2024-05-22/</link><description>对流亡中国商人郭文贵的刑事审判将于周三开始陪审团遴选，美国检察官指控郭文贵诈骗数千名投资者和支持者超过 10 亿美元。</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 10:04:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/legal/exiled-chinese-businessman-guo-wengui-goes-trial-fraud-2024-05-22/</guid></item></channel></rss>